<HL> Mazda Increases
@  1990-Model Prices
@  To Upgrade Image
@  ----
@  By Bradley A. Stertz
@  Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal </HL>
<DD> 08/23/89 </DD>
<SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J) </SO>
